Source Code:
LXI H, 4000H   ; HL points to 4000H
MOV A, M       ; Get first operand from 4000H into A
INX H          ; HL points to 4001H
SUB M          ; Subtract content of 4001H from A
INX H          ; HL points to 4002H
MOV M, A       ; Store result at 4002H
HLT            ; Terminate program execution

