| 0204H          | 23     | INX H    | -       | Increment HL to point 4001H      |
| 0205H          | 96     | SUB M    | -       | Subtract content of 4001H from A |
| 0206H          | 23     | INX H    | -       | Increment HL to point 4002H      |
| 0207H          | 77     | MOV M, A | -       | Store result from A into 4002H   |
| 0208H          | 76     | HLT      | -       | Halt execution                   |
